The paper discusses a neural re-ranking approach for ad-hoc search, which is a task related to information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the usage of neural network models, which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
